entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You defeated Lady Valarian's assassin and Jabba is pleased. Good work!
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Speak with Lady Valarian to receive reparations for the death of Bera Jeza.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: Hahahahaha....I knew it wasn't a mistake sending you. You may be future competition for my best bounty hunter.
